snippet.title: Walkabout Mini Golf - Oculus Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available on Oculus Quest & Rift!
Putt your way through beautifully designed courses, collect lost balls, challenge your friends and unlock bonus levels. Extremely realistic physics create the perfect experience for hardcore golfers and casual players alike. 
Oculus Quest: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/2462678267173943/
Oculus Rift: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/2328506790595457/
